{"tid":2189443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蒙古高官因保護蒙古語自殺，支共老屈精神病","createTime":"2020-09-05T01:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T05:22:23.000Z","uid":55628,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c3c9452cd2be2c13c9832cdd08755cf9d27f819","tid":2189443,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T01:53:52.000Z","msg":"內（南，下同）蒙古阿拉善盟政府辦公室一名蒙古族女官員蘇日娜（33歲），昨（4日）清晨在其住所墮樓身亡。警方指死者患有抑鬱症。不過，網絡流傳死者一份遺書顯示，蘇日娜死亡與近期蒙古族人保護蒙古語有關。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙古通遼市、烏拉特中旗等地，近日爆發蒙古族農牧民抗議，反對當局強推漢語教學。在過去一周，曾傳出多人在抗議時離奇墮樓身亡，但當局封鎖消息，連死者的姓名和背景資料都無法得知。<br />\n<br />\n蘇日娜是第四宗墮樓身亡事件，消息由其丈夫證實。長期關注農牧民維權的蒙古族學者忽必斯向自由亞洲電台證實：「阿拉善盟又有一位蒙古人自殺了，公務員，在政府單位工作。」另一名蒙古族人則指：「阿拉善盟有一位蒙古族婦女，因反對政府取消蒙古語教學，一氣之下跳樓身亡，具體情況仍在核實。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">     丈夫：醫院要求說妻子是抑鬱症復發     </span><br />\n<br />\n蘇日娜是中共阿拉善盟黨委，其丈夫名叫阿拉騰巴格那，在阿拉善盟左旗黨委工作。阿拉騰巴格那在微信語音留言說：「（妻子）因為壓力大，就跳樓了，<span class=\"red\">  但是醫院讓我說是因為抑鬱症    </span>，所以跳樓。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全文請瀏覽蘋果<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200905/RSTZUI6VCBCGLFEZZOFTVZUPXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200905%2FRSTZUI6VCBCGLFEZZOFTVZUPXA%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4xVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=acdbf433\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200905%2FRSTZUI6VCBCGLFEZZOFTVZUPXA%2F&h=f6fdeae8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200905/RSTZUI6VCBCGLFEZZOFTVZUPXA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共抹黑慣常伎倆，不過次次劇本都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad07380b62b6e3c047f419eababb5899b09aa01e","tid":2189443,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"抑鬱症<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c34788033715244b83ac2120362b723e104d23","tid":2189443,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:00:55.000Z","msg":"支共一定要死"},{"pid":"cad684702fa727e6a43316097fd56422b357e563","tid":2189443,"uid":214173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"回力鏢擊中陳X霖阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e68621a0857190d6af3b827626815d0f33495f4","tid":2189443,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:03:36.000Z","msg":"港豬家長：普教中好呀, 第時返大陸做有錢大陸佬生意"},{"pid":"82546712cd3a7794ca160ad4dc4af0a767c63b9f","tid":2189443,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad07380b62b6e3c047f419eababb5899b09aa01e","tid":2189443,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"抑鬱症<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"竹鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca4cfe6d6da27ac9757be97f046ada110e84d14","tid":2189443,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ad07380b62b6e3c047f419eababb5899b09aa01e","tid":2189443,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"抑鬱症<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"無新意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/21114004/macau.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F21114004%2Fmacau.png&h=3af46711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1996051/org/f5ce02358a0f36922accff71ace70a7f.jpg/9RUk_89sg6o1bzxeTXOdMkqh8CIM8-kPDVsK_Q1bCv0?v=w1920r16_